cs.MM, cs.CV, cs.SD, cs.CL, cs.IR 

The paper deals with multi-modal information in videos and audio, and specifically focuses on creating joint audio-visual embeddings for retrieval tasks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.MM (Multimedia), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.SD (Sound). The paper also involves natural language processing techniques for text-based retrieval, which could place it in cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
